name: THE TICKLE - Issue #17
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

#17 is the Halloween Issue, featuring Kajetan Obarski AKA Kiszkiloszki, Dylan Murphy AKA Pretty Bad & the cryptic mysteries of the Crypto Webcam project.

Featured writers this week are the novelist Joanne Rush and artist Maia Mellier, with an extract from her druidic collab with Aevin.

Created by artists Wily Guys (@guyswily) and Maia Mellier (@maiamellier)
